WEBVTT

00:00:00.951 --> 00:00:03.952
So people tell me I'm a nice person ...

00:00:06.020 --> 00:00:10.063
to the point where it's part
of my personal and professional identity

00:00:10.087 --> 00:00:14.426
that I'm so nice
and able to get along with anyone,

00:00:14.450 --> 00:00:17.684
even my most fierce opponents.

00:00:18.837 --> 00:00:21.047
It's like my "thing,"
it's what I'm known for.

00:00:21.071 --> 00:00:24.037
(Laughter)

00:00:24.061 --> 00:00:26.997
But what no one knows ...

00:00:29.063 --> 00:00:30.586
is that I was a bully.